statements: SELECT * FROM Backtesting_Trading_Strategies;
SELECT strategy_name, start_date FROM Backtesting_Trading_Strategies WHERE strategy_id = 1;
SELECT symbols, start_date, end_date FROM Backtesting_Trading_Strategies WHERE strategy_name LIKE '%Trend%';
SELECT * FROM Backtesting_Trading_Strategies ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT strategy_id, strategy_name, end_date FROM Backtesting_Trading_Strategies WHERE strategy_name = 'Mean Reversion';
SELECT * FROM Backtesting_Trading_Strategies WHERE strategy_id = 1;
SELECT strategy_name, start_date, end_date FROM Backtesting_Trading_Strategies WHERE strategy_name LIKE '%Trend%';
SELECT strategy_id, strategy_name FROM Backtesting_Trading_Strategies ORDER BY strategy_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM Backtesting_Trading_Strategies WHERE start_date > '2020-01-01' AND end_date < '2021-01-01';
SELECT strategy_id, symbols FROM Backtesting_Trading_Strategies WHERE symbols @> ARRAY['AAPL','GOOGL'];
SELECT * FROM strategy_results WHERE id = 1;
SELECT strategy_name, backtest_start_date, backtest_end_date FROM strategy_results;
SELECT * FROM strategy_results ORDER BY backtest_start_date DESC;
SELECT strategy_name, performance_metrics FROM strategy_results WHERE backtest_start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, strategy_name, backtest_end_date FROM strategy_results WHERE strategy_name LIKE 'Trend%';
SELECT * FROM strategy_results WHERE strategy_name = 'MACD' AND backtest_start_date > '2021-01-01'
SELECT strategy_name, backtest_start_date, backtest_end_date FROM strategy_results WHERE backtest_end_date < '2021-12-31' ORDER BY backtest_start_date DESC
SELECT id, strategy_name, performance_metrics->'Sharpe_Ratio' AS sharpe_ratio FROM strategy_results WHERE JSON_EXTRACT(performance_metrics, '$.CAGR') > 0.1
SELECT trade_id, TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, timestamp, NOW()) AS seconds_elapsed FROM trade_data WHERE symbol = 'GOOGL' ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT strategy_id, symbol, SUM(position_size) AS total_position_size FROM trade_data GROUP BY strategy_id, symbol HAVING total_position_size > 100
SELECT * FROM Strategy;
SELECT strategy_name, strategy_description, strategy_id FROM Strategy;
SELECT backtest_id, backtest_date, backtest_result FROM Backtest WHERE backtest_result > 1000;
SELECT trade_id, trade_symbol, trade_quantity FROM TradeData WHERE trade_quantity >= 100;
SELECT strategy_name, backtest_date, trade_quantity FROM Strategy JOIN Backtest ON Strategy.strategy_id = Backtest.strategy_id JOIN TradeData ON Backtest.backtest_id = TradeData.backtest_id;
SELECT * FROM Strategy ORDER BY strategy_id ASC;
SELECT strategy_name, strategy_description FROM Strategy WHERE strategy_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM Backtest WHERE backtest_result > 1000 ORDER BY backtest_date DESC;
SELECT trade_symbol, trade_quantity, trade_price FROM TradeData WHERE backtest_id = 3;
SELECT MAX(backtest_result) AS max_result FROM Backtest;
SELECT * FROM trading_strategies;
SELECT strategy_name, start_date, end_date FROM trading_strategies;
SELECT strategy_id, strategy_name FROM trading_strategies WHERE strategy_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM strategy_data ORDER BY data_date DESC;
SELECT strategy_id, MAX(result_value) AS max_result FROM backtesting_results GROUP BY strategy_id;
SELECT * FROM trading_strategies WHERE strategy_id = 1
SELECT strategy_name, start_date FROM trading_strategies WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01'
SELECT strategy_id, MAX(data_value) AS max_value FROM strategy_data GROUP BY strategy_id
SELECT * FROM backtesting_results WHERE result_value > 100 ORDER BY result_date DESC, result_id ASC
SELECT queue_id, queue_date FROM processing_queue WHERE strategy_id = 3 ORDER BY queue_date
SELECT * FROM Trades WHERE trade_quantity > 100;
SELECT trade_symbol, trade_price FROM Trades ORDER BY trade_price DESC;
SELECT t.trader_name, s.strategy_name FROM Traders t JOIN Strategies s ON t.trader_id = s.strategy_id;
SELECT trade_symbol, AVG(trade_price) AS avg_price FROM Trades GROUP BY trade_symbol;
SELECT trade_date, trade_quantity, trade_price FROM Trades WHERE trade_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31';
SELECT * FROM Strategies;
SELECT strategy_name, strategy_description FROM Strategies WHERE strategy_id = 1;
SELECT trader_name, trader_location FROM Traders ORDER BY trader_id DESC;
SELECT trade_symbol, trade_quantity, trade_price FROM Trades WHERE trade_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT result_id, result_profit FROM BacktestResults WHERE result_profit > 1000 ORDER BY result_profit DESC;
